      <dd class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-700 sm:col-span-2 sm:mt-0">A <a href="/specifications/dublin-core/dcmi-terms/#contributor">second property</a> with the same name as this property has been declared in the <a href="http://purl.org/dc/terms/">dcterms: namespace</a>.  See the Introduction to the document <a href="/specifications/dublin-core/dcmi-terms/">DCMI Metadata Terms</a> for an explanation.</dd>
    </div>
    
  </dl>
</article>

      
        










  
    
    
    
    
      
    
  





  

