      <dd class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-700 sm:col-span-2 sm:mt-0">Recommended practice is to use either a non-literal value representing a language from a controlled vocabulary such as ISO 639-2 or ISO 639-3, or a literal value consisting of an IETF Best Current Practice 47 [<a href="https://tools.ietf.org/html/bcp47">IETF-BCP47</a>] language tag.</dd>
